				},
				"string" : "{{gtClass:BlScripter}} is the framework for scripting and verifying UI interactions in Glamorous Toolkit. It lets users create reproducible scenarios that simulate user actions (clicks, typing, keyboard shortcuts, scrolling) and assert UI state."
			},
