				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The main entry point is {{gtClass:BlScripter}} . Steps are the building blocks: they model  actions or assertions. The scripter manages a {{gtClass:BlSpace}} internally — the UI is live and pulsed between steps to let layout, animations, and tasks settle."
