										"string" : "- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#id:|label=#selector}} — find by element ID\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#//|label=#selector}} — descendant search (like CSS descendant selector)\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onChildAt:|label=#selector}} — nth child (1-based)\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onBreadthFirstChildOfClass:|label=#selector}} — breadth-first search by class\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#@|label=#selector}} — filter by block predicate\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onModel|label=#selector}} — target the scripter's model instead of an element\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onSelf|label=#selector}} — target the current element\n- {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onSpace|label=#selector}} / {{gtMethod:TBlDevScripterTarget>>#onSpaceRoot|label=#selector}} — target the space"
